8	Primary diagnostic procedure	<ol>\r\n\t<li>Read and understand customers claim. Clarify if needed.</li>\r\n\t<li>Provide visual inspection of the device. Pay special attention to:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin-left:40px">\r\n\t<li>case (covers) their corners and joints.</li>\r\n\t<li>ports (USB, jack, micro SD card reader slot, etc).</li>\r\n\t<li>display (please refer to the &ldquo;display mechanical damages clarification file&rdquo; in order to provide better</li>\r\n\t<li>diagnostic procedures).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Clarify device serial number and needed FW version.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If device doesn&rsquo;t power on (doesn&rsquo;t load into the main menu):</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Remove the back cover (or disassemble device) and measure the battery voltage (charge or replace if needed).</li>\r\n\t<li>Try to power on.</li>\r\n\t<li><a href="http://service.pocketbook-int.com/devices/626+%20%7C%20Touch%20Lux%203/Internal%20micro%20SD%20card%20replacement">Replace the internal memory micro SD card</a>&nbsp;with bootable known good micro SD card for this particular model.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Or insert into the card reader of the device a micro SD card with SDSN (SD card serial number) detection.</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Try to power on.</li>\r\n\t<li>&nbsp;If no result please use Unit Replacement Program procedure.</li>\r\n\t<li>After receiving the replacement unit reset the serial number and update FW to the needed version.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If device powers on:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Provide diagnostic of customers claim and try to solve it.</li>\r\n\t<li>Possibly you will have to update device FW in order to solve the problem.</li>\r\n\t<li>If no solution without PCBA or display replacement is available, please use Unit Replacement Program procedure.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Additionally:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n\t<li>Provide additional visual inspection of the display (pay special attention to the lines, dots, spots and front light</li>\r\n\t<li>quality).</li>\r\n\t<li>Check touch screen reaction (run &lsquo;Scribble&rsquo; application and try to draw a grid).</li>\r\n\t<li>Check Wi-Fi connection.</li>\r\n\t<li>Check micro SD card slot.</li>\r\n\t<li>Check PC connection.</li>\r\n\t<li>Update FW to the latest version.</li>\r\n</ol>	2017-12-06 14:26:35.474657+00	2017-12-07 10:08:50.005863+00	11
